Class ArithmeticRuleExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.linqs.psl.model.rule.arithmetic.expression.ArithmeticRuleExpression

  • public class ArithmeticRuleExpression
extends Object
    Container for components of an arithmetic rule formula. Full equality checks (when two expressions are the equal, but not the same refernce) are epensive.
